    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of engineering, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS top-end refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile shifts, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the suspension geometry is dialed, and the powertrain remains exceptionally responsive. A purist-spec M3 ready for immediate performance duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
