    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable Differential Lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive Double VANOS overhaul and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering and neutral handling balance characteristic of the marque. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain exhibits excellent compression and smooth power delivery across the entire rev range. A true driver\u2019s specification for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical pedigree and analog feedback.",
